column2: SELECT &&& + cast(p.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& + cast(p.objId as varchar(#)) + &&& as objID, p.run, p.rerun, p.camcol, p.field, p.obj, p.type, dbo.fPhotoTypeN(p.type) as type, p.ra, p.dec, pz.z, pz.zerr, pz2.photozcc2, pz2.photozerrcc2, p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.Err_u, p.Err_g, p.Err_r,p.Err_i,p.Err_z FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#, # , #) n INNER JOIN PhotoPrimary as p on n.objid = p.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz as pz on p.objid = pz.objid LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz2 as pz2 on p. objid = pz2.objID
